title: [Vornavian Coast, Coastal Cliffs]
description: The path follows the edge of the cliff face here, providing a magnificent view of the ocean in the moonlight.  Small shapes skitter across the shore far below, unrecognizable in the dim light.

The path follows the edge of the cliff face here, providing a magnificent view of the ocean.  Seagulls fly from the tops of the cliffs to the shore far below in search of a meal.  Crows perch among the crags of the cliffs, waiting for unwary sand crabs to venture past the shore line.
